# ⚙️ Requirements

- Java 17+
- Maven 3+
- Linux / macOS / Windows

---

# 🚀 Build & Run

## Build project
```bash
mvn clean install

## Run project
```bash
java -cp target/classes com.billpayment.app.Application
```


1. Cash In
CASH_IN <amount>
Ex: CASH_IN 1000000

2. Create Bill
CREATE_BILL <id> <type> <amount> <dueDate(dd/MM/yyyy)> <provider>
Ex: CREATE_BILL 1 ELECTRIC 200000 25/10/2026 EVN

3. List Bills
LIST_BILL

4. Update Bill
UPDATE_BILL <id> <type> <amount> <dueDate> <provider>
Ex: UPDATE_BILL 1 3000000 EVN 2026-11-01

5. Delete Bill
DELETE_BILL <id>

6. Search Bill by Provider
SEARCH_BILL_BY_PROVIDER
Ex: SEARCH_BILL_BY_PROVIDER EVN

7. Pay Bill
Single payment
PAY <billId>
Ex: PAY 1

Multiple payment
PAY <id1> <id2> <id3>
Ex: PAY 1 2 3

8. Schedule Payment
SCHEDULE <billId> <dd/MM/yyyy>
Ex: SCHEDULE 2 28/10/2026

- Create payment with status PENDING
- A cronjob will run every day at 00:00 to check if there are any PENDING payments with due date equal to current date, if yes, the payment will be processed and status will be updated to PAID

9. List Payment History
LIST_PAYMENT

10. Bills by Due Date
DUE_DATE

11. Exit
EXIT
```